{"version": 2, "width": 85, "height": 42, "timestamp": 1774001112, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/zsh", "TERM": "screen-256color"}}
[0.016547, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[J"]
[0.017093, "o", "\r\n  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  │   nur — collective security intelligence                    │\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  │   Three hospitals. Same ransomware. None of them know.      │\r\n  │   nur lets them figure it out — without revealing who       │\r\n  │   they are.                                                  │\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n"]
[4.023697, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║  2:17 AM — Ohio Children's Hospital\r\n"]
[4.023855, "o", "  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[6.039419, "o", "\r\n  LockBit ransomware. EHR encrypted. NICU monitors offline.\r\n"]
[6.848359, "o", "\r\n  The IR team has IOCs from the attack — malicious IPs,\r\n"]
[7.658396, "o", "\r\n  command-and-control domains, file hashes.\r\n"]
[8.464285, "o", "\r\n\r\n  But they don't know:\r\n"]
[9.274773, "o", "    - Is anyone else seeing this same campaign?\r\n"]
[9.792654, "o", "    - Does CrowdStrike catch T1490 (VSS deletion)?\r\n"]
[10.301342, "o", "    - What actually worked at other hospitals that got hit?\r\n"]
[10.815689, "o", "\r\n\r\n  They can't ask. Sharing incident data could trigger\r\n"]
[11.627554, "o", "\r\n  mandatory reporting. Their lawyer won't sign off.\r\n"]
[12.438489, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[12.438639, "o", "  Unless... what they share isn't incident data at all.\r\n"]
[16.257986, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║  Starting nur\r\n"]
[16.258138, "o", "  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[20.281365, "o", "\r\n  Server running. Now let's seed it with data from\r\n"]
[21.097984, "o", "\r\n  multiple hospitals — each contributing anonymously.\r\n"]
[23.918376, "o", "\r\n  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n"]
[23.918412, "o", "\r\n"]
[24.927666, "o", "\r\n  First, hospitals upload their vendor evaluations.\r\n"]
[25.742648, "o", "\r\n  Each one evaluated CrowdStrike, SentinelOne, etc.\r\n"]
[26.548315, "o", "\r\n  nur strips all free text, keeps only scores + categories.\r\n"]
[27.363017, "o", "\r\n"]
