[142.154738, "o", "  \r\n                                              A             B\r\n    Vendor                         CrowdStrike Falcon   SentinelOne\r\n    ========================================================\r\n    Weighted Score                            ?             ?\r\n    Confidence                     insufficient  insufficient\r\n    Eval Count                                0             0\r\n    Category                                edr           edr\r\n"]
[142.154766, "o", "    Price Range                    >$60/endpoint/yr  $30-60/endpoint/yr\r\n  \r\n"]
[147.188236, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║  The proof: anyone can verify\r\n"]
[147.188369, "o", "  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[149.193149, "o", "\r\n  The CISO's board asks: 'How do we know these numbers\r\n"]
[150.003465, "o", "\r\n  are real? How do we know you didn't make them up?'\r\n"]
[150.815815, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[150.815948, "o", "  Answer: cryptographic proof.\r\n"]
